copy

public static void copy(com.vividsolutions.jts.geom.CoordinateSequence src,
                        int srcPos,
                        com.vividsolutions.jts.geom.CoordinateSequence dest,
                        int destPos,
                        int length)
Copy length coordinates in src staring at srcPos to dest at destPo. This method silently truncates the number dimension if the src or dest does not have that many coordinates

Parameters:
src - The source coordinates.
srcPos - The source position.
dest - The destination coordinates.
destPos - The destination position.
length - The number of coordinates to copy.

orientationIndex

public static int orientationIndex(double x1,
                                   double y1,
                                   double x2,
                                   double y2,
                                   double x,
                                   double y)
Returns the index of the direction of the point q relative to a vector specified by p1-p2.

Parameters:
p1 - the origin point of the vector
p2 - the final point of the vector
q - the point to compute the direction to
Returns:
1 if q is counter-clockwise (left) from p1-p2
